SUMMARY:St. Paddy's Day Celebration! (DJ and Dancing) (Tuesday\, March 17t
 h)
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nGood day everyone\,\n\nPlease join
  us for a fantastic **St. Paddy's Celebration\;** as we mix\, mingle\, dan
 ce the night away to all our favorite songs!\n\n\\*Joined by my other soci
 al groups too\; so we can anticipate a terrific turn out with lots of frie
 ndly peers to enjoy dinner and the lively dance floor!\n\n**Date:** Tuesda
 y March 17th\, 2026\n**Location:** 747 Mt. Pleasant (Smoke Show)\n\n**\\*M
 eet us inside Smoke Show between 7:30 pm and 9:00 pm**\n\\*If you have to 
 arrive after that\, still let the front door staff know you are with **Ste
 ve's group** so they can direct you to us!\n\n(Event Details Below)\n\nSin
 cerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host )\n\nEvent Details:\n**St. Pad
